# Omninuera
**Offer of Internship – AI Intern**

Date: [OFFER_DATE]

To: [INTERN_FULL_NAME]  
Address: [INTERN_ADDRESS]

Dear [INTERN_FULL_NAME],

We are pleased to offer you an internship with Omninuera for the position of **AI Intern**. This letter summarizes the primary terms of your internship. Please review and confirm acceptance by signing and returning a copy of this letter.

Position and Duration
- Role: AI Intern.
- Duration: 3 months, beginning on [START_DATE] (placeholder).
- Work location: Fully remote (based in Bengaluru).
- Employment type: Internship (stipend-based). This internship is a temporary educational/work experience and is not guaranteed employment with Omninuera upon completion.

Reporting
- You will report to: [REPORTING_MANAGER_NAME], [REPORTING_MANAGER_TITLE] (placeholder).

Compensation
- Stipend: INR 10,000 per month (stipend).
- Payment schedule: Stipend will be paid monthly, on or before the [PAYMENT_DAY] of the following month (or within 7 business days after month-end), subject to completion of any required onboarding paperwork and time reporting. Taxes, if any, will be handled in accordance with applicable laws.

Duties / Responsibilities
- You will assist with tasks related to AI research, model development, data preparation, testing, documentation, and other duties as assigned by your reporting manager.
- You are expected to perform your duties professionally and to meet goals and deadlines agreed upon with your manager.
- Specific projects, deliverables, and expectations will be provided by your reporting manager.

Working Hours / Expectations
- As a remote intern, you are expected to be available for core overlapping hours: [CORE_HOURS] IST (placeholder), and to coordinate with your manager on weekly schedules.
- Expected commitment: approximately [WEEKLY_HOURS] hours per week (placeholder), though actual hours may vary by project need. Flexibility may be required.
- You must maintain regular communication with your reporting manager and attend scheduled meetings.

Confidentiality / NDA
- You will be required to sign and comply with Omninuera’s Confidentiality and Non-Disclosure Agreement (NDA). You must not disclose or use any confidential information except as necessary to perform your internship duties.

Intellectual Property / Assignment of Inventions
- You acknowledge that all inventions, discoveries, works of authorship, developments, improvements, and other work product created or developed by you during the internship that relate to Omninuera’s business or result from work performed for Omninuera will be the exclusive property of Omninuera.
- You agree to execute any documents reasonably requested by Omninuera to assign or perfect Omninuera’s rights in such intellectual property.

Termination / Notice
- Either party may terminate this internship with [TERMINATION_NOTICE_PERIOD] days' written notice (placeholder). Omninuera may terminate the internship immediately for cause, including but not limited to breach of this agreement, breach of the NDA, misconduct, or violation of company policies.
- Upon termination, you must return Omninuera property and delete or return confidential materials as directed.

Background Checks (if applicable)
- This offer may be conditional upon completion of a satisfactory background check and verification of your educational and employment history, where applicable. By accepting this offer, you consent to such checks if required.

Compliance with Local Laws
- This internship will be conducted in compliance with applicable local laws and regulations. You are responsible for ensuring you satisfy any legal requirements to perform remote work from Bengaluru.

Contact for HR
- For any questions regarding this offer, stipend payments, or HR-related matters, please contact HR at: [HR_CONTACT_EMAIL] (placeholder) or [HR_CONTACT_PHONE] (placeholder).

Miscellaneous
- This letter, along with any referenced agreements (e.g., NDA), constitutes the complete terms of your internship offer. This internship is stipend-based and does not guarantee future employment.
- No modification of this offer will be effective unless made in writing and signed by an authorized representative of Omninuera.

Acceptance
If you agree to the terms above, please sign below and return a scanned copy of this letter.

Sincerely,

For Omninuera

